hivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Nh%E1%BA%ADp-H%C3%A0nh-Ch%C3%A2u/poem-RaTSZaUHzh49rWc6QXWeqw">Nhập Hành Châu - 入衡州</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Khi%C3%AAm-%C3%8Dch/T%E1%BA%A1-L%C6%B0%E1%BB%A1ng-Qu%E1%BA%A3ng-t%E1%BB%95ng-%C4%91%E1%BB%91c-Kh%E1%BB%95ng-c%C3%B4ng-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-G2tpt59CWHsnu6SB1WllHA">Tạ Lưỡng Quảng tổng đốc Khổng công kỳ 1 - 謝兩廣總督孔公其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Khi%C3%AAm-%C3%8Dch/author-Kf5yfK5iK_BR3H2g75GaXQ">Phạm Khiêm Ích</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Duy/T%E1%BB%91ng-ph%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-t%C3%B4n-s%C6%B0-quy-Tung-s%C6%A1n/poem-OhvytOX9odjpa-uKqEzW-Q">Tống phương tôn sư quy Tung sơn - 送方尊師歸嵩山</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Duy/author-9f1Hth0gmM_PXzGNXg5Fog">Vương Duy</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ho%C3%A0ng-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-Ki%C3%AAn/V%C5%A9-trung-%C4%91%C4%83ng-Nh%E1%BA%A1c-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-l%C3%A2u-v%E1%BB%8Dng-Qu%C3%A2n-s%C6%A1n-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-ieiQUIjqJWpJG4TdwWQ2Rg">Vũ trung đăng Nhạc Dương lâu vọng Quân sơn kỳ 1 - 雨中登岳陽樓望君山其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ho%C3%A0ng-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-Ki%C3%AAn/author-wRpSKwqTcKjFpinJIe2YPg">Hoàng Đình Kiên</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/Xu%C3%A2n-h%C3%A0n-c%E1%BA%A3m-th%C3%A0nh/poem-XhYxxJWcQTx3BDOT1UySXA">Xuân hàn cảm thành - 春寒感成</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/author-JHbQVfC53E2lRJL-xE616A">Nguyễn Khuyến</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
